rs]]<br></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*input|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*options|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*option label|closed}}</p>\n<br></blockquote>\n<h2>Other<br></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*accountable|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*autoname|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*captcha|closed}}</p>\n{{*layout|closed}}\n<p>{{*send|closed}}</p>\n{{*table of contents|closed}}\n<p>{{*thanks|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</p>'),(5549,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',301,1,'<p>Value options for a set of [[Pointer]] cards. Can itself be a Pointer or a [[Search]]. [[http://wagn.org/Pointer|Learn about setting options on Pointers.]]</p>'),(5555,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',66,1,'<p>People can&nbsp;<strong>sign up with no approval process</strong>&nbsp;if you allow \"Anyone\" to [[/card/options/Account_Request|create account requests]], and give \"Anyone\" the [[/admin/tasks |global permission]] to create accounts.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Newly registered users will be sent an email with a password and the following details:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email Subject<br></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*signup+*subject|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email Message</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*signup+*message|closed;type:PlainText}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>As the email is sent, the<strong> person signing up will be sent here</strong>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<div>HTTP://<em>(YOUR WAGN\'S DOMAIN)</em>{{+*thanks}}</div>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(5557,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',56,1,'<p>People can <strong>invite new users via email</strong> if they have the&nbsp;[[/admin/tasks|global permission]] to \"create accounts\".</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Newy invited users will be sent an email with a password and the following details:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email subject</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*subject|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email message</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*message|type:PlainText}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Email from</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*from|type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>After sending an invitation, you\'re taken here:</strong><span><strong></strong></span></p>\n<blockquote>\n<div>HTTP:// <em>(YOUR WAGN\'S DOMAIN) </em>{{+*thanks}}</div>\n</blockquote>'),(5566,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',63,1,'<p>People can <strong>request an account</strong> via a \"Sign Up\" link if you allow \"Anyone\" to [[/card/options/Account_Request|create account requests]].</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Unless [[*signup|approved automatically]], the <strong>request will be emailed to</strong>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{+*to|closed;type:Phrase}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>and the<strong> requester will be redirected here:</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<div>HTTP:// <em>(YOUR WAGN\'S DOMAIN) </em>{{+*thanks}}</div>\n</blockquote>\n<div>You can <strong>approve/deny account requests [[Account Request|here]]</strong>.</div>'),(5573,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',297,1,'<div>Sets define a group of cards to which settings can apply. [[http://www.wagn.org/wagn/Setting|Learn more about settings.]]</div>'),(5581,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',458,1,'2'),(5582,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',443,1,''),(5583,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',459,1,''),(5584,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',460,1,'2'),(5585,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',444,1,'2'),(5586,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',150,1,'<p>[[http://wagn.org/John_Abbe|My card on wagn.org]]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[[new]] is where we talk about building this default content for new Wagns.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Setting+*type+by_name|item:name}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Some helpful cards:</p>\n<p>{{Cardtype descriptions|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Cardtype help text|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Cardtype forms|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Right forms that aren\'t subtabs|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{all non-star cards|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{cards by type|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{+*watching|open}}</p>'),(5590,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',410,1,'<p>Since so many capabilities are built with Wagn itself, new  installations come with several hundred cards by default. Most of them  are listed here (not including many cards that make up some of the plus  cards below). The default cards themselves are actually maintained on  en.dwagn.org</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>[[Cardtypes]]</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Each includes a description card, and links here to relevant documentation.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Administrative<br></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Account Request]]</p>\n<p>[[Cardtype]]</p>\n<p>[[Role]]</p>\n<p>[[Set]]</p>\n<p>[[Setting]]</p>\n<p>[[User]] &mdash; and [[User+*type+*accountable]] makes it possible for them to have accounts.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Data types</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Basic]]<br>[[Phrase]]<br>[[PlainText]]<br>[[Image]] &mdash; and [[Image+*right+*default]] makes any new card ending in +Image to be of type Image.<br>[[File]]</p>\n<p>[[Pointer]]</p>\n<p>[[Search]]</p>\n<p>[[Toggle]]<br>[[Number]]<br>[[Date]]<br>[[HTML]] &mdash; and [[HTML+*type+*default]] sets new ones to be editable only by Administrators.</p>\n<p>[[Ruby]] &mdash; but they\'re turned off by default</p>\n<p>[[Script]] &mdash; but they\'re turned off by default</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Sidebar<br></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Menu]]<br>[[Administrator links]]<br>[[Config]] &mdash; in Administrator links</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Account-related</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Roles and Accounts<br></h2>\n<p>Each includes a description card, and links here to relevant documentation.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Anyone]]<br>[[Anyone signed in]]<br>[[Administrator]]</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>[[Anonymous]]</p>\n<p>[[Wagn Bot]]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>Other<br></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[Cards with accounts]] &mdash; lists account-holding cards (typically [[Users]], included on [[*account]]<br>[[Invite Success]] &mdash; See [[/wagn/account#Administering%20accounts]] for more on this and the next two.<br>[[Request Sent]]<br>[[Signup Success]]</p>\n<p>[[Role+*type+*content]] &mdash; form for Role cards</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>For ordering searches</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>So that you can do things like \\[[User+*type+by create]] (people in the order they registered an account).</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[[by name+*right+*content]]<br>[[by update+*right+*content]]]]<br>[[by create+*right+*content]]]]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Miscellaneous</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>[[Home]] &mdash; default front page</li>\n<li>[[email config+*right+*content]] &mdash; form for emails sent via [[flexible email]]. Help text is [[email config+*right+*edit help]].</li>\n<li>[[discussion+*right+*default]] &mdash; so that any [[plus card]] ending with +[[discussion]] allows comments<br>[[tags]] &mdash; for tagging, e.g. in the [[Related tab]]. [[tags+*right+*default]] makes any card +tags a Pointer</li>\n<li>[[Form submission thanks]] &mdash; see [[thank you messages]]</li>\n<li>[[description]] &mdash; for the built in descriptions of cardtypes and roles<br>[[Default Layout]] &mdash; the default layout, specified by [[*all+*layout]]. See [[custom layouts]].</li>\n<li>Regarding [[notifications]]:<br> {{watcher instructions for related tab|closed}}</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>[[Star cards]] (everything below)<br></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{star cards}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(5592,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',461,1,'[[radio]]\n[[checkbox]]\n[[select]]\n[[multiselect]]\n[[list]]'),(5593,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',462,1,'radio'),(5597,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',119,1,'<h1>[[_left+*roles|{{_left|name}}\'s roles]]<br></h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{_left+*roles|item:link}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>[[_left+*watching|{{_left|name}} is watching]]</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{_left|name}} will receive email whenever these cards (or cards of types listed here) are changed. [[http://wagn.org/wagn/Notification|Learn more about notifications.]]</p>\n<p>{{_left+*watching|item:change}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>[[_left+*created|{{_left|name}} created]]</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{_left+*created|item:change}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>[[_left+*editing|{{_left|name}} has edited]]</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{_left+*editing|item:change}}</p>\n</blockquote>'),(5598,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',95,1,'{\"edited_by\": \"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"update\"}'),(5603,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',38,1,'{\"include\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5604,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',42,1,'{\"included_by\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5605,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',44,1,'{\"linked_to_by\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5606,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',40,1,'{\"link_to\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5607,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',34,1,'{\"part\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5608,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',36,1,'{\"plus\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5611,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',447,1,'{\"referred_to_by\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5612,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',450,1,'{\"refer_to\":\"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5613,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',97,1,'{\"member\": \"_self\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5619,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',395,1,'{\"type\": \"File\",\n \"sort\": \"update\"\n}'),(5621,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',223,1,'/* fixit - once \"type\" accepts card defs:\n{\"or\": \n {\"and\": {\"plus\": [\"*watcher\", {\"refer_to\": \"_self\"} ], \"not\": {\"type\": \"Cardtype\"} } },\n {\"type\": {\"plus\": [\"*watcher\", {\"refer_to\": \"_self\"} ], \"type\": \"Cardtype\"} }\n}\n*/\n\n{\"plus\": [\"*watcher\", {\"refer_to\": \"_self\"} ],\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5624,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',161,1,'{\"type\": \"Cardtype\",\n \"append\": \"*type\",\n \"sort\": \"name\"\n}'),(5625,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',463,1,''),(5626,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',464,1,''),(5627,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',299,1,'<p>The type of editor for a set of [[Pointer]] cards.</p>'),(5638,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',404,1,'<p>(Learn more about [[http://www.wagn.org/wagn/internationalization|translating Wagn into other languages]].)</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Here are all of the cards to translate into another language. Be sure not to edit the name of any cards that begin with a star (*), or their content unless you are explicitly asked to do so here:</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Cardtypes<br></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Cardtype <strong>names</strong> themselves should be translated, as well as the <strong>description</strong> of each Cardtype:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Cardtype+*type+by name}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Edit help<br></h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>All of the customizable edit help <strong>contents</strong>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*edit help+*right+by name}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Sidebar</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>names</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of these cards in the sidebar:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Menu|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Administrator links|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Config|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Account-related</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>description</strong> of each Role, and the two account cards:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Anyone|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Anyone signed in|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Administrator|closed}}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>{{Anonymous|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Wagn Bot|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> of \"cards with accounts\" and the <strong>content</strong> of \"*account\".</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Cards with accounts|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*account|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of these:</p>\n<blockquote>{{Invite Success|closed}}\n<p>{{Request Sent|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Signup Success|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> of these. Make sure you update the reference at the end of the first three to the corresponding new name of one of the three cards just above.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*invite|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*request|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*signup|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Role+*type+*default|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Related tab\'s subtabs</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> only of these:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*incoming+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*outgoing+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*plusses+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*community+*right+*content|closed}}<br>{{*account+*right+*content|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{watcher instructions for related tab+*right+*content|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{Cardtype+watcher instructions for related tab+*type plus right+*content|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{watcher instructions for related tab|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h1>Miscellaneous</h1>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> of *title, which appears in most web browsers\' title bar:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*title|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> of the default home card &mdash; make sure to change both the name of the card itself, and update *home to the new name:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Home|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*home|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Similarly, change the <strong>name</strong> of \"Default Layout\" and the reference to it in \"*all+*layout\". Also, translate Home, Recent, and the credit text (\"Wheeled by...\" in the <strong>content</strong> of \"Default Layout\":</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Default Layout|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{*all+*layout|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Just the <strong>names</strong> of these cards (used to order search results):</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{by name|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{by update|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{by create|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>name</strong> and <strong>content</strong> of this card:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{Form submission thanks|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>names</strong> only of these cards:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{discussion|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{tag|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{description|closed}}</p>\n<p>{{email config|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>The <strong>content</strong> of this card (the cards named do not exist and don\'t need to):</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>{{*input+*right+*option|closed}}</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>'),(5640,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',465,1,'{\"sort\":\"update\", \"dir\":\"desc\", \"view\":\"change\"}'),(5641,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',466,1,'{\"match\":\"$keyword\", \"sort\":\"relevance\"}'),(5642,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',467,1,'{\"link_to\":\"_none\"}'),(5643,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',468,1,''),(5644,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',469,1,''),(5645,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',470,1,''),(5646,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',471,1,''),(5647,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',472,1,''),(5648,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',473,1,''),(5649,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',474,1,''),(5713,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',221,1,'{\"extension_type\": \"User\"}\n/* note -- this syntax is not yet deprecated but will be before Wagn 2.0 */'),(5717,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',478,1,''),(5718,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',479,1,''),(5719,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',480,1,''),(5720,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',481,1,''),(5721,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',482,1,''),(5722,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',483,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5723,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',484,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5724,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',485,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5725,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',486,1,'{\"left\":{\"type\":\"_left\"}, \"right\":\"_right\"}'),(5726,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',487,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5727,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',488,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5728,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',489,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5729,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',490,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5730,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',491,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5731,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',492,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5732,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',493,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5733,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',494,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5734,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',495,1,'[[Administrator]]'),(5735,'2012-01-26 12:37:04',496,1,'[[Anyone Signed I